body: "\n# Watering Schedules for Tomato Beds\n\nRaised beds drain faster than open ground, so tomatoes need a steady rhythm\nrather than occasional soaking.\n\n## Observations\n\n- [requirement] Water deeply once per week during the growing season #watering\n- [gotcha] Shallow daily watering trains roots to stay near the surface #watering\n\n## Relations\n\n- relates_to [[Composting Basics]]\n"
